                    </div>
                    <span>We are very pleased to announce that 'The Minimalist Garden' has been awarded the Inspirational Garden Book of the Year 1999 by the Garden Writers' Guild in London.<P>Mark Fletcher, Executive Editor, Mitchell Beazley</span>
                  
              
